lead_paragraph: LUU--My. Resident of Briarcliff Manor, NY, formerly of Houston, TX, was a wife, daughter, sister, aunt and friend. My passed away on September 25, 2015 at the age of 41. Her vibrant spirit will be missed by all who knew her. www.crowdrise.com/MyLuuFund 1/3
